# ============================================================
# FPGA 开源工具链 — .gitignore
# 策略：只追踪脚本/文档/工程源码，不追踪工具二进制和构建产物
# 工具链在新机器上按 docs/SOP-macos-fpga-toolchain.md 重建
# ============================================================

# --- oss-cad-suite 预编译包 ---
tools/oss-cad-suite/

# --- nextpnr-xilinx 外部仓库（从 openXC7 克隆，按 SOP 重建）---
tools/nextpnr-xilinx-src/

# --- prjxray 外部仓库（从 f4pga 克隆，按 SOP 重建）---
tools/prjxray/

# --- Python 缓存 ---
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo

# --- macOS 垃圾文件 ---
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
._*

# --- 编辑器 ---
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.vscode/
.idea/

# --- 构建中间文件 ---
*.o
*.a
*.so
*.dylib

# --- FPGA 工程生成文件 ---
projects/*/*.json
projects/*/*.fasm
projects/*/*.frames
projects/*/*.bit
projects/*/*.bin
